CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1962, pg. A14 reads: "...Chi Delta Mu supper dance, last Saturday at the Hilton..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women and men, including Corrine Harris, Jody Harris, Miriam Sharpe Fountain, Morris Fountain, Sr. and Dr. Reginald Dixon, seated at banquet table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
